For the ones that cant find a place for the serial:
first make sure you open the rar with winrar or 7zip.
In quicktime player window use menu Edit /Preferences/Register

in the window that pops-up, use the info inside serial key txt:
Registered to: xxxxxxx (replace xxxx with the ones on txt file)
Registration code: xxxxxxxxxxxxxx (replace xxx with the ones on txt file)

Hope it helps.
